column4: - From label information - SETE STAR SEPT are the finest purveyors of avantgarde noise/grind in our age. This is an antithesis of normality based on the vast history of Japanese extreme music. Exhilarating, draining and autistic noise. Over the last two years, SETE STAR SEPT have focused on putting out a slew of releases; this collection features the vinyl output: split 12\" w/ GENERIC DEATH, split 10 w/ NOISE, split 7\" w/ PENIS GEYSER, split 7\" w/ CSMD, split 7\" w/ SATAN, split 7\" w/ ROTGUT, 4-way split 7\", \"gero me\" 10\" and a live set from KFJC, clocking in at 75 minutes total. This is a very sick CD.
